## Data Source Attribution

All underlying data used in WEI calculations remains the property of the
respective organisations:

- UN Women — data.unwomen.org
- World Bank — genderdata.worldbank.org
- UNESCO — uis.unesco.org
- UNODC — unodc.org
- WHO — who.int/data/gho
- ILO — ilostat.ilo.org
- OECD — oecd.org
- IPU — data.ipu.org
- NCRB — ncrb.gov.in (India)

Use of these datasets is subject to each organisation's respective
terms and conditions.

